                       Golf in Belek, TURKEY 
                   
                  
                  
                  Local Knowledge & Experience 
Book direct with Bilyana Golf Holidays 
                 
               
             
             
              
               
                  We are a Belek Golf Resort Specialist selling packages to UK & European golfers. During the rise of Beleks popularity we have enjoyed steady growth & success and have achieved a very high status becoming one of the leaders in providing 5 star All Inclusive golf packages to Belek. Our client feedback is excellent and our solid foundation here in Antalya City near the Belek resort is something we are very proud of. Our motto is ‘Knowledge and Experience’ and the partnership between our Head Office here in Antalya and our UK Office is our great stength. 
                 > For more information see About Bilyana Golf tab   
               
             
             
               
                  
                   
                   
                   
                   
                  
                   
                  
                  
                   
                    
                     
                     
                     
                     
                    
                     
